Addnewblog = Generates a new blog or if blog with that id already exists it lets to edit it.
if a new blog is created in Addnewblog it is saved in the database simultaneously as well.


Save Blog = Saves a Card for the Blog. (blog is already saved in the database)

on clicking on "save drafts" the document will be updated with the content added by the user.


myblogs is replaced by blogwithid